bash -c ' [ -n "$(xdotool search --onlyvisible --desktop --name "windowname")" ] && [ "$(xdotool getactivewindow)" = "$(xdotool search --onlyvisible --desktop --name "windowname")" ] && xdotool windowminimize "$(xdotool search --onlyvisible --desktop --name "windowname")" || xdotool windowactivate "$(xdotool search --onlyvisible --desktop --name "windowname")" || "appname" '
